			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Well my post on the perma camp didn't come through yet, but I just did the shadow book part.  Time to dispell rumors.  Unless you can ACTUALLY charm the Shadow man, the 2 ihs thing doesn't work.  I did Screaming Terror, tried to just hand over, etc.  Save yourself the greif.<BR>
<BR>
Now.  The ice comet thing is probably right, the trick is to keep them out of melee.  I fough them all day for nothing, until I did this:  When the necro ones spawn, they cast their pet.  Let them start.  We all know how long THAT takes.  Then Ignite their bones, and follow up with a shock of poison.  This will put them in slow run away mode.  One last SoP and bam!  No melee, you get your book.  This worked the first 2 times I tried it on them, after that I was like: 3 hours, got my book, OUTTA HERE.   <BR>
<BR>
So follow my three simple steps and the book will be yours.  And this all started because I got an SMR and had too much int.....  oh well, bye bye harvester :)<BR>
<BR>
Secef Electriboogaloo<BR>
Got Necro?<BR>
&lt;edroh 'eht rules!&gt;<BR>
see ya on the fennin side
